cs.DC, cs.CC, cs.SE, cs.CR, cs.PL 

This paper discusses the performance evaluation of commercial Cloud services, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC) and Cloud Computing (cs.CC). It also involves software engineering (cs.SE) for designing and conducting experiments, as well as cryptography and security (cs.CR) for evaluating the security of Cloud services. Finally, it may also relate to programming languages (cs.PL) for developing Cloud applications.
